# 🖋️ Wireframe & Mockup Descriptions

## 🏠 Homepage Mockup
- Hero banner: “Amane: A Safe Space to Report, Heal, and Connect”
- Floating red “Panic Mode” button (top-right corner)
- 3 quick paths: “Report Now”, “Talk to Someone”, “Find Help Near Me”
- Language switcher (bottom-left)
- Footer: “Built with love for Ethiopian survivors”

## 📝 Reporting Portal Wireframe
- Step-by-step form:
  1. “What happened?” → dropdown
  2. “Who was involved?” → auto-suggest
  3. “Do you need immediate help?” → triggers Panic Mode
- Upload options: photo, audio, text
- Save Draft button (local storage)

## 🌳 My Healing Tree Dashboard
- Central tree graphic — grows leaves as user completes milestones
- Milestones: “First Report”, “Connected to Counselor”, “Attended Event”
- Export as printable poster: “I am growing stronger every day.”

## 🗺️ Resource Map Mockup
- Interactive map of Ethiopia
- Filters: Type (Legal/Counseling/Shelter), Language, Accessibility
- Each pin shows: Verified badge, rating, transport tips
- Click pin → opens modal with contact info + directions

## 🧘 Wellness Corner Mockup
- Floating “Breathe” button (always visible)
- Modal with:
  - Guided breathing (Amharic audio)
  - Nature sounds (Simien Mountains, Blue Nile Falls)
  - Affirmation cards (“You are safe. You are not alone.”)

